Program: The Why Factor
Title: Why do we forget the things we’ve learned?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswrkg
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 17 Sep 2018
Have you ever been captivated by a book, full of stories you never knew, revelled in that new knowledge …and then forgotten it all? If the answer is yes, take heart; you are not alone. Why is it we remember some facts easily, and others slip away? In this week’s Why Factor Sandra Kanthal asks why do we forget the things we’ve learned. Image: Brain Concept. Credit: BSIP / UIG via Getty Images Show less